# Per-Dockerfile ignore (BuildKit). Patterns are evaluated against the build
# context, which is the repository root (see docker-compose.yml `context:`).
# Keeps the context small and reproducible — host build outputs are never
# shipped into the image; the build stage recompiles everything from source.

# Build outputs
**/target/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/.flattened-pom.xml
**/dependency-reduced-pom.xml

# Frontend deps (the build reinstalls them inside the image)
**/node_modules/

# VCS / CI
.git/
.github/

# IDE / editor / OS noise
.idea/
.vscode/
**/*.iml
**/.DS_Store

# Agent / tooling local state
.claude/
**/logs/
docs/_build/
